*Dolazimo* ranije nego što smo planirali. (We are coming earlier than we had planned.)

Planiramo da *dolazimo* u petak. (We are planning to come on Friday.)

*Dolazimo* li u petak ili subotu? (Are we coming on Friday or Saturday?)

Izgleda da ćemo *dolaziti* kasnije nego što smo planirali. (It looks like we're going to be coming later than we had planned.)

Ne znamo tačno kada ćemo *dolaziti*. (We don't know exactly when we will be coming.)